## Project Structure

```
docs-fumadocs/
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router
│   ├── docs/              # Documentation pages
│   ├── api/               # API routes (search, chat)
{%- if fumadocs_llms_txt == 'enabled' %}
│   ├── llms.txt/          # LLM summary endpoint
│   ├── llms-full.txt/     # Full docs for LLMs
│   └── llms.mdx/          # Per-page MDX access
{%- endif %}
├── components/            # React components
├── content/
│   └── docs/             # MDX documentation files
├── lib/                  # Utility functions
{%- if fumadocs_openapi == 'enabled' and api_module == 'enabled' and api_languages %}
├── openapi/              # OpenAPI specifications
{%- endif %}
└── static/               # Static assets
```

## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `pnpm dev` | Start development server |
| `pnpm build` | Build for production |
| `pnpm start` | Start production server |
| `pnpm lint` | Run ESLint |
| `pnpm typecheck` | Run TypeScript checks |
{%- if fumadocs_typedoc == 'enabled' %}
| `pnpm docs:sdk` | Generate TypeDoc SDK docs |
{%- endif %}
{%- if fumadocs_search_provider == 'algolia' %}
| `pnpm search:sync` | Sync search index to Algolia |
{%- endif %}

{%- if fumadocs_llms_txt == 'enabled' %}

## AI/LLM Endpoints

This documentation site includes AI-friendly endpoints:

- `/llms.txt` - Summary of documentation for LLMs
- `/llms-full.txt` - Complete documentation in plain text
- `/docs/*.mdx` - Per-page Markdown access

These endpoints make it easy for AI assistants to consume and reference the documentation.
{%- endif %}

